summary: Northern Ireland's football team has been making headlines recently. In the UEFA Nations League, they played to a scoreless draw against Belarus. Despite the disappointment of not winning, player Callum Marshall expressed his reluctance to play in empty stadiums due to the lack of fan support. In another match, Northern Ireland narrowly missed out on the Victory Shield after a hard-fought battle. However, they redeemed themselves with a resounding 5-0 victory over Bulgaria, with Isaac Price scoring a hat-trick. The team's performance against Bulgaria earned praise in the media, with Belfast Live giving positive player ratings and highlighting the impressive win.

name: Jimmy Carter
summary: Former US President Jimmy Carter made history by becoming the first former president to turn 100 years old. Shortly after his birthday, he fulfilled his wish of voting in the presidential election. Carter, who voted in Georgia, cast his ballot for Kamala Harris. This was a significant moment, as Carter is a longtime supporter of Harris and has expressed his admiration for her work. Images of Carter waiting in line to vote went viral, highlighting his dedication to civic duty and the importance of exercising one's right to vote.

summary: In the realm of fashion and celebrity, Gigi Hadid has graced the headlines with headlines surrounding her personal life and her return to the Victoria's Secret runway. Hadid's tribute to her close friend, Taylor Swift, during the fashion show adds a personal touch to the coverage, as does her fashion statement with her rugby shirt. These articles collectively paint a vibrant picture of Hadid's multifaceted persona and her influence within the worlds of fashion and entertainment.

name: Full moon October 2024
summary: In October 2024, the Hunter's Moon, also known as the Super Hunter's Moon, will be the largest and most spectacular full moon of the year. Scheduled to occur on October 9, this celestial event derives its name from the traditional hunting season in the Northern Hemisphere. As the biggest supermoon of 2024, it will appear noticeably larger and brighter than usual, providing an ideal opportunity for stargazing enthusiasts and astrologers alike. The full moon in Aries during this period is believed to carry significant astrological implications, encouraging individuals to embrace boldness, ambition, and new beginnings.
